    {
      "ruleId": "hz.web.e8a4712ba467f54c.rule.3",
      "text": "Authors who follow these guidelines should incorporate this phrase near the beginning of their document: The key words \"MUST\", \"MUST NOT\", \"REQUIRED\", \"SHALL\", \"SHALL NOT\", \"SHOULD\", \"SHOULD NOT\", \"RECOMMENDED\", \"MAY\", and \"OPTIONAL\" in this document are to be interpreted as described in RFC 2119 .",
